<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Notifikasi Akun</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f7fb;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background-color: #f4f7fb;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .email-card {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15613F 0%, #0F462D 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #1F2937;
    }

    .code-container {
      background-color: #F3F4F6;
      border: 1px dashed #9CA3AF;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #15613F;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4B5563;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .warning {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6B7280;
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    }

    .email-footer {
      padding: 24px 30px;
      background-color: #F9FAFB;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6B7280;
    }

    .email-footer strong {
      color: #15613F;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-card">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h2>UIKA LIFE CAMPUS</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="greeting">Halo, {{name}}!</div>

        <div class="message">
          Berikut adalah kode atau informasi login Anda. Harap jangan bagikan informasi ini kepada siapa pun untuk
          menjaga keamanan akun Anda.
        </div>

        <div class="code-container">
          {{link}}
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
          Jika Anda tidak meminta informasi ini atau merasa ada aktivitas mencurigakan, segera abaikan pesan ini atau
          reset kata sandi Anda.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        Salam hangat,<br>
        Universitas Ibn Khaldun
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>